        <h3 class="text-align-center"><strong>Do you have a dynamic short story?</strong></h3><hr><h4 class="text-align-center black-heading" style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing:inherit;color:rgb(19, 19, 19);font-family:RussischSansRegular;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:30px;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</h4><h4 class="text-align-center black-heading" style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing:inherit;color:rgb(19, 19, 19);font-family:RussischSansRegular;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:30px;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;">As seen in<strong> </strong><a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/short-story-content-roadmap-writers-barry-josephson-1235993535/"><strong>Variety</strong></a>:&nbsp;</h4><p class="text-align-center">&nbsp;</p><p class="text-align-center"><span style="color:#000000;">This short story challenge is open to original <strong>short stories of any genr</strong>e that can captivate the reader in no more than 50 pages.&nbsp;</span></p><p class="text-align-center"><span style="color:#000000;"><strong>The winning short story will be granted a prize of $7000!</strong></span></p>
